446
00:30:18,265 --> 00:30:19,682
Świetnie.

447
00:30:20,473 --> 00:30:22,057
Pokaż mi bukiety.

448
00:30:26,890 --> 00:30:27,973
Panie Morgan.

449
00:30:28,057 --> 00:30:30,473
